properties.areaText:
In May of 2013, OR-7
entered his current
residence area.
Since then, he found
 a mate, they had pups,
and together they
are known as the
"Rogue Pack."

In November of 2011,
OR-7 wandered for over
a month around the
Sky Lakes area, which would
become his home later,
in 2013.

In January of 2012, OR-7 crossed into California
and spent about one year there. OR-7 was the
first gray wolf seen in California in a century!
He returned to Oregon in April of 2013.

On September 30, 2011,
Wolf OR-7 decided to
break away from his pack.
